medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="huny_3-1721785946594.png" alt="huny_3-1721785946594.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="huny_4-1721785958645.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/140806i1E5EA8D42C0EADA7/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="huny_4-1721785958645.png" alt="huny_4-1721785958645.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Please help me with how to read the text of Custom Code.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;thank you&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Huny&lt;/P&gt;</content>
