    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/component-scrap/qaq-p/13770306</id>
    <title>Component scrap</title>
    <updated>2024-07-24T14:17:41.727000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>michalkoska</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/856908</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi all,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;we implemented Operational scrap in a routing and next step is setup Component scrap. We have also assembly scrap on SFG level, which should be overwritten by operational and component scrap.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Operational scrap is working correct, but my question is, if there is possibility to setup component scrap based on quantities in Operations.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Example:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;quantity on order is 260, plus assembly scrap = 400&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="michalkoska_1-1721823125521.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/141002iEC57F52D2B717A18/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="michalkoska_1-1721823125521.png" alt="michalkoska_1-1721823125521.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Also operational quantity is calculated correctly, is lower and lower in next step as process proceed&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="michalkoska_0-1721823092361.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/141001iC82C95408D16B459/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="michalkoska_0-1721823092361.png" alt="michalkoska_0-1721823092361.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;but component quantities are calculated from base quantity when production order was created(260pcs)&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="michalkoska_2-1721823241867.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/141003i8EBF64FE0025E5DF/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="michalkoska_2-1721823241867.png" alt="michalkoska_2-1721823241867.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;is there any possibility that component quantities will be calculated from reduced quantities?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;thank you for your advice,&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/component-scrap/qaq-p/13770306"/>
    <published>2024-07-24T14:17:41.727000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
