    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I have a Brazilian customer that has two others plants, one in UK and the other in PT and needs the invoice documents to be forwarded to the tax agencies in real time, for a public project, what would be the suggestion, since the customeralready has already a system that generates invoice and communicates with the authorities. Do you suggest an API is made with a sales document in SAP that generates an invoice in the legacy system and does the latter communicate with the tax agency and return the invoice in SAP or does SAP Public delivers everything directly using DRC?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In terms of time and work, what would be the suggestion?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Remembering that it is a public project and we only have 2 months to complete.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
