      <name>Haaroon_Daya</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/59098</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;SAP S4Hana public cloud standard sends invoices to the project manager after a billing document is completed. I understand this is configured in the output determination settings application.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Billing Document:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Haaroon_Daya_0-1722000545811.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/142578i8B4D879147BEFA94/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Haaroon_Daya_0-1722000545811.png" alt="Haaroon_Daya_0-1722000545811.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Output items:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Haaroon_Daya_3-1722000651547.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/142581i7ABCCEBA5F6501D8/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Haaroon_Daya_3-1722000651547.png" alt="Haaroon_Daya_3-1722000651547.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Email example:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Haaroon_Daya_2-1722000620921.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/142580i1C57A46364CA4001/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Haaroon_Daya_2-1722000620921.png" alt="Haaroon_Daya_2-1722000620921.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Output determination settings:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Haaroon_Daya_1-1722000596792.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/142579i1C8599F39F87482B/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Haaroon_Daya_1-1722000596792.png" alt="Haaroon_Daya_1-1722000596792.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We are now looking for the invoice to be sent via email to a particular individual/ group of individuals where the invoice is created out of a specific cost center in SAP S4hana public cloud.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Is there any configuration (manage your solution) or settings (output parameter determination) that we could make use off within SAP. We did check through these options but we could not see where we could set this up for a specific cost center&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Please provide possible solutions to achieve the above&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;#COE,#DE01&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/financial-management-q-a/setting-up-billing-document-attachment-email-settings-by-cost-center/qaq-p/13773623"/>
    <published>2024-07-26T15:40:22.775000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
